            <title>[SOLR-11272] EmbeddedSolrServer does not set the path for known SolrRequestHandlers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-11272</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;EmbeddedSolrServer&lt;/tt&gt; does not set the path for known &lt;tt&gt;SolrRequestHandlers&lt;/tt&gt; in the query request context.  This leads to a &lt;tt&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/tt&gt;.  Patch and test coming in pull request.&lt;/p&gt;

